\": \"\\\"I know that he is married now and has settled down.\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it's a tough thing to do to punish him twice and if he's managed to successfully turn his life around after being sent to prison and to qualify and to be playing sport at the highest level, then I actually wish him the best of luck.\\\"\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tough thing\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1431}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1507}, {\"ngram\": \"prison\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1541}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1580}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest level\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1601}, {\"ngram\": \"luck\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde met the girl on Facebook, and flew to England to meet her with full knowledge of her age.\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1699, \"end\": 1706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7659928074170215, \"rank\": 0.16909729086728628, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1660}, {\"ngram\": \"the girl\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1673}, {\"ngram\": \"Facebook\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"full knowledge\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1738}, {\"ngram\": \"her age\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He only served 12 months in a Dutch prison and has since returned to compete internationally.\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1844, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"12 months\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1775}, {\"ngram\": \"a Dutch prison\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Women's groups have condemned the decision to allow Van de Velde to compete at the Games, and criticised his selection by the Netherlands.The Timesreports the 29-year-old is staying at a different location rather than with the other competitors in the athletes' village.\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 2116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Women's groups\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 1860}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1888}, {\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1910}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1934}, {\"ngram\": \"his selection\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1964}, {\"ngram\": \"the Netherlands\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1983}, {\"ngram\": \"The Timesreports\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2000}, {\"ngram\": \"a different location\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2051}, {\"ngram\": \"the other competitors\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2090}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other organisations, including the British Olympic Association would not have allowed the beach volleyball player onto their Olympic team because of their own safeguarding rules.\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2153, \"end\": 2180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other organisations\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2137}, {\"ngram\": \"the beach volleyball player\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2231}, {\"ngram\": \"their Olympic team\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2255}, {\"ngram\": \"their own safeguarding rules\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2295}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Radcliffe however seemed to take back those comments, replying to a post criticis